<h1 align="center">CTF Activity Stream</h1>

<p align="center">
  <a href="https://github.com/hungraw/ctf-stream/releases"><img src="https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/hungraw/ctf-stream?style=for-the-badge&color=blue" alt="Release"></a>
